WEBVTT

1
00:19:29.610 --> 00:19:30.900 
谢谢你 先生
Thank you, sir.

2
00:19:30.990 --> 00:19:32.700 
丘吉尔先生 您有什么议程吗
Mr. Churchill, what's your agenda?

3
00:19:32.780 --> 00:19:36.320 
议程 先来一杯宝禄爵香槟吧
The agenda? A glass of Pol Roger.

4
00:19:36.410 --> 00:19:38.200 
- 再见 - 看这里 先生
- Cheers. - Over here, sir!

5
00:19:38.290 --> 00:19:39.670 
你们 你们会如愿拍到照片的
You'll-you'll have your pictures.

6
00:19:39.750 --> 00:19:41.050 
首相先生
Prime Minister.

7
00:19:41.120 --> 00:19:42.330 
安东尼
Anthony.

8
00:19:42.420 --> 00:19:44.170 
国王怎么样
How is the king?

9
00:19:44.250 --> 00:19:45.620 
很焦虑
Anxious.

10
00:19:46.050 --> 00:19:49.300 
他是不会原谅我当年支持
He's never forgiven me for supporting

11
00:19:49.720 --> 00:19:52.850 
他哥哥和沃利斯·辛普森结婚的事了
his brother's marriage to Wallis Simpson.

12
00:19:52.930 --> 00:19:54.890 
你每周只要和他见一面就好
You only have to meet him once a week.

13
00:19:54.970 --> 00:19:56.970 
哦 那就像要你一周
Oh, but that's like saying you only have to have

14
00:19:57.060 --> 00:19:59.110 
拔一次牙一样
your tooth pulled once a week.

